description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines for our listeners to get a chance to humble the personalities with "Slander the Breakfast Club". Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a young man who is seeking cosmetic procedure to look like his selfie filters and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
